1
00:00:12,012 --> 00:00:13,555
A wedding dress!

2
00:00:14,890 --> 00:00:16,391
Are there 11 couples?

3
00:00:27,402 --> 00:00:28,862
Standing before you

4
00:00:28,946 --> 00:00:31,990
are 11 married couples.

5
00:00:33,575 --> 00:00:35,619
Five of these couples

6
00:00:35,702 --> 00:00:38,622
- have multiple children.
- Multiple children?

7
00:00:38,705 --> 00:00:40,374
The other 6 couples

8
00:00:40,457 --> 00:00:42,709
have no children.

9
00:00:42,793 --> 00:00:44,878
What makes this so extreme

10
00:00:44,962 --> 00:00:46,547
is that some here have no kids.

11
00:00:46,630 --> 00:00:47,923
Completely childless.

12
00:00:48,465 --> 00:00:51,385
This must be tough.
There are twice as many people to read.

13
00:00:51,468 --> 00:00:54,388
That's way too many.
They have to read 22 people.

14
00:00:55,264 --> 00:00:58,225
Read the couples' fates
and their child-related fortunes,

15
00:00:59,559 --> 00:01:01,687
then find the couples
with multiple children.

16
00:01:03,021 --> 00:01:05,899
How are we to guess who has kids
with a minor on our team?

17
00:01:05,983 --> 00:01:07,234
Come on.

18
00:01:07,317 --> 00:01:08,944
Mommy's got this.

19
00:01:10,320 --> 00:01:12,281
I have a child of my own,

20
00:01:12,364 --> 00:01:14,866
and most of my clients are moms.

21
00:01:14,950 --> 00:01:16,743
I've met moms with many kids,

22
00:01:16,827 --> 00:01:17,911
so I was confident.

23
00:01:19,162 --> 00:01:21,039
I'm good at reading who's had an abortion

24
00:01:21,123 --> 00:01:23,458
or who's had or will have a baby.

25
00:01:23,542 --> 00:01:24,543
But…

26
00:01:25,836 --> 00:01:29,047
the first match was tough
because we couldn't agree on things.

27
00:01:29,131 --> 00:01:31,466
Honestly, I'd basically given up.

28
00:01:32,801 --> 00:01:34,469
But I was still determined to survive.

29
00:01:36,013 --> 00:01:37,556
I'm pretty confident.

30
00:01:37,639 --> 00:01:41,602
Last week, my Granny spirit told me
to put seaweed on the altar in my shrine.

31
00:01:41,685 --> 00:01:44,563
That means Grandma Samshin
is involved.

32
00:01:44,646 --> 00:01:48,233
And today, we got a question
that needs Grandma Samshin's powers.

33
00:01:48,984 --> 00:01:50,527
I'm sure we'll go through.

34
00:01:52,029 --> 00:01:53,655
You will be given 100 minutes.

35
00:01:53,739 --> 00:01:56,491
If you think you have the correct answer,

36
00:01:56,575 --> 00:01:58,327
go to the Well of Truth,

37
00:01:58,410 --> 00:01:59,494
ring the bell,

38
00:01:59,578 --> 00:02:02,247
and you'll find out if you're right.

39
00:02:03,373 --> 00:02:04,750
If your answer is correct,

40
00:02:05,417 --> 00:02:07,294
the moon will appear in the well.

41
00:02:08,003 --> 00:02:11,256
Fate Readers, please begin the reading.

42
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:15,844
Right away? Just like that?

43
00:02:15,927 --> 00:02:17,596
Hmm?

44
00:02:17,679 --> 00:02:20,474
Noh Seulbi is always quick to move.

45
00:02:20,557 --> 00:02:22,768
Totally. She just charges straight in.

46
00:02:23,602 --> 00:02:25,520
Do couples with many children

47
00:02:25,604 --> 00:02:28,398
give off a different aura?

48
00:02:28,482 --> 00:02:29,983
I'm sure they do.

49
00:02:34,279 --> 00:02:36,198
With couples who have many children,

50
00:02:36,281 --> 00:02:38,116
I can tell just from their faces.

51
00:02:38,200 --> 00:02:41,453
I can tell if the mom
is a boy mom or a girl mom.

52
00:02:55,550 --> 00:02:57,260
Grandma Samshin.

53
00:02:57,886 --> 00:02:59,930
She's 1 of the deities I serve,

54
00:03:00,013 --> 00:03:01,848
so I'm good at this kind of thing.

55
00:03:07,270 --> 00:03:09,606
Oh, she must be here.
Grandma Samshin's taking over.

56
00:03:09,690 --> 00:03:12,192
Grandma Samshin's here.

57
00:03:20,367 --> 00:03:22,411
- His gaze has changed.
- Yes.

58
00:03:22,494 --> 00:03:23,787
He must have a feeling.

59
00:03:25,080 --> 00:03:27,165
My Granny spirit showed me images

60
00:03:27,749 --> 00:03:31,461
of couples holding a baby,
not knowing what to do.

61
00:03:35,966 --> 00:03:38,927
TEAM BLACK TORTOISE

62
00:03:39,010 --> 00:03:40,720
Grandma Samshin…

63
00:03:46,685 --> 00:03:50,313
My Guardian spirit
plays the role of Grandma Samshin too.

64
00:03:50,856 --> 00:03:53,275
And the scissors I carry around
are the very ones

65
00:03:53,358 --> 00:03:56,778
she uses to cut umbilical cords.

66
00:03:56,862 --> 00:03:59,197
That's why I carry around those scissors.

67
00:04:01,366 --> 00:04:03,201
So I took them with me.

68
00:04:04,995 --> 00:04:06,997
- Young Master Plum Blossom.
- He's here.

69
00:04:17,841 --> 00:04:20,719
I walked around the couples
with the Samshin scissors

70
00:04:20,802 --> 00:04:23,138
and I could get a vague idea
of whether they have kids.

71
00:04:24,389 --> 00:04:28,852
I then snapped the scissors
in front of some couples.

72
00:04:32,230 --> 00:04:34,232
I did that to see

73
00:04:34,316 --> 00:04:36,610
if I could hear babies crying.

74
00:04:38,236 --> 00:04:39,571
After that…

75
00:04:50,081 --> 00:04:52,417
I smell baby formula.

76
00:04:56,338 --> 00:04:59,090
I opened up all my senses,

77
00:04:59,174 --> 00:05:01,718
and suddenly I could smell baby formula.

78
00:05:04,012 --> 00:05:06,640
But since there were so many people,

79
00:05:06,723 --> 00:05:09,017
I couldn't tell

80
00:05:09,100 --> 00:05:11,394
who the formula smell was coming from.

81
00:05:11,478 --> 00:05:14,564
So I walked back and forth
between them for a while,

82
00:05:14,648 --> 00:05:16,733
and I stopped in front of the couple

83
00:05:16,817 --> 00:05:18,985
where I caught that formula smell again.

84
00:05:27,994 --> 00:05:30,413
I was sure she has a child.

85
00:05:33,124 --> 00:05:36,086
TEAM AZURE DRAGON

86
00:05:36,169 --> 00:05:37,879
Shall we do a reading separately first?

87
00:05:37,963 --> 00:05:41,258
-Yes. Let's discuss after.
-Let's do it separately first.

88
00:05:41,341 --> 00:05:45,554
- Let's see if we have overlapping answers.
- All right.

89
00:05:45,637 --> 00:05:47,222
Team Azure Dragon.

90
00:05:47,305 --> 00:05:49,182
Lee Sobin's a bit quiet, isn't she?

91
00:05:49,266 --> 00:05:51,434
Yeah, she wasn't going for it.

92
00:05:51,518 --> 00:05:54,229
But she needs to prove herself
on this one.

93
00:05:54,938 --> 00:05:56,731
This is her moment to deliver.

94
00:06:01,528 --> 00:06:03,613
I wasn't much help in the first match

95
00:06:03,697 --> 00:06:06,658
because my Granny spirit had gone home,

96
00:06:06,741 --> 00:06:10,328
so I was determined to do well this time.

97
00:06:12,622 --> 00:06:14,541
She is fated to be a boy mom.

98
00:06:15,959 --> 00:06:18,336
During my initiation rite,
the first fortune I told was,

99
00:06:18,420 --> 00:06:20,088
"There's a baby in your tummy."

100
00:06:20,171 --> 00:06:22,299
ANOINTING TO RECEIVE
DEITIES AND BECOME A SHAMAN

101
00:06:22,382 --> 00:06:25,427
They say I have strong ties
with Grandma Samshin.

102
00:06:25,510 --> 00:06:28,430
That means I'm good
at reading fortunes related to babies.

103
00:06:28,513 --> 00:06:31,349
Are they able to stay together
without children?

104
00:06:32,058 --> 00:06:34,936
Or do they need children to stay together?

105
00:06:35,020 --> 00:06:37,022
That was my approach to this question.

106
00:06:37,606 --> 00:06:41,693
Jeong Gihwan, 45, Choi Bogyeong, 46.
Do they have more than 1 child?

107
00:06:48,658 --> 00:06:50,994
Do you have your answers?
Shall we discuss?

108
00:06:51,077 --> 00:06:52,912
Why don't we start with the first couple?

109
00:06:53,913 --> 00:06:57,083
Number 1, Hwang Hyeonhwan and his wife.

110
00:06:57,917 --> 00:07:00,587
What I'm getting from couple number 1

111
00:07:00,670 --> 00:07:02,631
is that they're like friends.

112
00:07:03,840 --> 00:07:06,217
But I got the sense that they fight.

113
00:07:06,301 --> 00:07:07,469
My initial reading is

114
00:07:07,552 --> 00:07:10,221
that they do have a child.

115
00:07:10,305 --> 00:07:12,265
- Me too.
- They have a child?

116
00:07:12,349 --> 00:07:16,144
The compatibility of this first couple is…

117
00:07:16,227 --> 00:07:18,813
They're both incredibly stubborn.

118
00:07:18,897 --> 00:07:20,732
- They clash.
- They clash hard when they do,

119
00:07:20,815 --> 00:07:22,776
- but when it's good, they're great.
- Yes.

120
00:07:22,859 --> 00:07:24,694
The husband's energy is stagnant,

121
00:07:24,778 --> 00:07:27,572
but the wife's cards show fire,

122
00:07:27,656 --> 00:07:30,241
so she gets pregnant easily.

123
00:07:30,325 --> 00:07:35,205
For them, I got the Three of Cups,
which symbolizes the womb.

124
00:07:35,288 --> 00:07:37,666
There's a card that symbolizes the womb?

125
00:07:38,416 --> 00:07:41,878
I also got the Birds,
and birds flock, you know.

126
00:07:41,961 --> 00:07:43,672
So their kids are like sparrows.

127
00:07:43,755 --> 00:07:46,341
That's how I felt, so I marked number 1
as a couple with children.

128
00:07:46,424 --> 00:07:47,425
Oh.

129
00:07:48,134 --> 00:07:50,053
Sparrows hatch a lot of eggs.

130
00:07:50,136 --> 00:07:52,347
She saw a womb in the cards for number 1.

131
00:07:52,430 --> 00:07:54,557
-Ah.
-How about you?

132
00:07:55,100 --> 00:07:57,060
To me, number 1 is…

133
00:07:58,019 --> 00:08:00,063
a maybe.

134
00:08:04,776 --> 00:08:07,737
This is when things get confusing.

135
00:08:07,821 --> 00:08:10,323
When 2 people say "yes"
but 1 of them says "no."

136
00:08:11,074 --> 00:08:13,243
Team Azure Dragon might argue a lot.

137
00:08:18,623 --> 00:08:22,168
Why do I keep seeing the wife
with a pregnant belly?

138
00:08:22,252 --> 00:08:25,797
Sobin, can you check
number 1 for me again?

139
00:08:32,345 --> 00:08:36,433
A GREEN FLAG SIGNALS NEGATION

140
00:08:36,516 --> 00:08:37,809
Uh-huh.

141
00:08:40,270 --> 00:08:42,981
But honestly,
Sobin doesn't seem like herself today.

142
00:08:43,064 --> 00:08:45,567
She's not her usual self.

143
00:08:48,153 --> 00:08:50,071
I keep losing my flow today.

144
00:08:51,072 --> 00:08:52,907
Even my obanggi
are not working.

145
00:08:52,991 --> 00:08:54,784
This round just isn't going my way.

146
00:08:55,493 --> 00:08:56,828
This is bad.

147
00:08:57,871 --> 00:08:59,080
I'm totally off today.

148
00:08:59,914 --> 00:09:01,249
I'm totally off today.

149
00:09:06,463 --> 00:09:08,381
What? No, Sobin…

150
00:09:08,465 --> 00:09:10,383
Sobin's in bad form.

151
00:09:11,092 --> 00:09:12,927
I can't see anything right now.

152
00:09:13,011 --> 00:09:15,055
- Don't give in. Try again.
- I'm done for.

153
00:09:15,138 --> 00:09:16,890
I'll draw your obanggi, then.

154
00:09:16,973 --> 00:09:18,308
Let me try.

155
00:09:20,185 --> 00:09:22,020
Here you go.

156
00:09:23,730 --> 00:09:26,357
A BLUE FLAG SIGNALS NEGATION

157
00:09:26,441 --> 00:09:28,276
This means no children.

158
00:09:28,359 --> 00:09:30,570
My obanggi can't be trusted right now.

159
00:09:31,613 --> 00:09:33,948
Why is my Granny spirit so angry?

160
00:09:34,866 --> 00:09:38,078
I could feel something was off
with me today.

161
00:09:38,161 --> 00:09:40,872
There are days
when you just can't read fortunes.

162
00:09:40,955 --> 00:09:43,792
So I figured
something must've upset my Granny.

163
00:09:43,875 --> 00:09:46,086
She'd basically gone on strike today.

164
00:09:48,088 --> 00:09:50,298
I think my Granny spirit clocked out.

165
00:09:51,257 --> 00:09:53,009
Her Granny spirit went home.

166
00:09:55,929 --> 00:09:57,514
Oh, no.

167
00:09:57,597 --> 00:09:59,557
Sobin is completely deflated.

168
00:10:00,350 --> 00:10:03,311
No wonder she was so quiet.

169
00:10:03,394 --> 00:10:05,814
- It must be a bad day for her.
- Oh, dear…

170
00:10:06,564 --> 00:10:08,024
She's not getting any readings.

171
00:10:09,609 --> 00:10:12,570
When I go to get my fortune told,

172
00:10:12,654 --> 00:10:15,365
even the good shamans say,
"I can't see anything today."

173
00:10:15,448 --> 00:10:17,992
Right, this is not her day. It can happen.

174
00:10:18,076 --> 00:10:19,702
They say their Granny spirit's angry.

175
00:10:20,286 --> 00:10:24,415
It must be really tough for shamans
when they can't see anything.

176
00:10:24,499 --> 00:10:25,959
It must drive them crazy.

177
00:10:26,042 --> 00:10:27,919
- They become helpless.
- Ah.

178
00:10:28,753 --> 00:10:30,588
She must be devastated.

179
00:10:32,507 --> 00:10:36,094
"Why won't you help me today,
Granny? Why won't you speak?"

180
00:10:36,177 --> 00:10:39,139
I was upset with her,
and I guess slightly resentful.

181
00:10:43,226 --> 00:10:45,228
They seem lost.

182
00:10:48,565 --> 00:10:49,566
Goodness.

183
00:10:55,113 --> 00:10:56,364
TEAM WHITE TIGER

184
00:10:56,447 --> 00:11:00,076
We must discuss
the most likely candidates.

185
00:11:00,160 --> 00:11:02,662
Number 1. They have children, right?

186
00:11:02,745 --> 00:11:03,830
Number 1.

187
00:11:03,913 --> 00:11:05,999
I think they have multiple kids.

188
00:11:06,082 --> 00:11:08,251
Do you all agree?

189
00:11:08,334 --> 00:11:10,461
Number 1.

190
00:11:10,545 --> 00:11:13,089
We'd missed an answer
in the previous match

191
00:11:13,173 --> 00:11:15,425
because I didn't listen to them,

192
00:11:15,508 --> 00:11:18,678
so I decided to be more accepting
of my teammates' opinions.

193
00:11:21,181 --> 00:11:23,850
A RED FLAG SIGNALS AFFIRMATION

194
00:11:23,933 --> 00:11:26,644
I also think that number 1 has children.

195
00:11:28,897 --> 00:11:30,773
Do we all agree?

196
00:11:30,857 --> 00:11:31,858
No, I'm not sure.

197
00:11:31,941 --> 00:11:34,444
- You're uncertain?
- I'm confused about 1 thing.

198
00:11:34,944 --> 00:11:36,946
They're incredibly incompatible.

199
00:11:37,864 --> 00:11:40,283
-Yet they're still together.
-Something makes it work.

200
00:11:40,366 --> 00:11:42,452
-They could be staying for the kids.
-Yes.

201
00:11:42,535 --> 00:11:45,079
-They'd split if they didn't have kids.
-Yes.

202
00:11:45,163 --> 00:11:47,081
Why don't we confirm with the well?

203
00:11:49,042 --> 00:11:50,585
Ask about couple number 1.

204
00:11:50,668 --> 00:11:52,295
-Shall we?
-Yeah, let's ask.

205
00:11:52,378 --> 00:11:54,505
- You're unsure about them, right?
- Yeah.

206
00:11:54,589 --> 00:11:56,507
- Then go for it. I trust you.
- Okay.

207
00:11:56,591 --> 00:11:58,760
- We must ask when we're not sure.
- Right.

208
00:12:03,264 --> 00:12:05,767
-They're going already?
-What?

209
00:12:05,850 --> 00:12:06,976
What's going on?

210
00:12:07,060 --> 00:12:09,354
Team White Tiger's fast.

211
00:12:20,114 --> 00:12:21,449
TEAM WHITE TIGER

212
00:12:21,532 --> 00:12:26,746
COUPLE 1 HWANG HYEONHWAN,
YANG EUNYEONG

213
00:12:43,763 --> 00:12:46,099
- The moon appeared.
- They got the moon.

214
00:12:47,350 --> 00:12:49,269
- This is crazy.
- Wow.

215
00:12:49,352 --> 00:12:50,853
They got it right away.

216
00:12:52,146 --> 00:12:53,481
Okay, they got it right.

217
00:12:53,564 --> 00:12:55,233
COUPLE 1 HAS MULTIPLE CHILDREN

218
00:12:55,316 --> 00:12:57,443
They're staying for the kids.

219
00:12:57,527 --> 00:13:00,154
- Right?
- Yes. We were right.

220
00:13:00,780 --> 00:13:02,865
They have no choice.

221
00:13:02,949 --> 00:13:05,243
Without the kids,
they can't stay together.

222
00:13:05,326 --> 00:13:07,203
COUPLE 1

223
00:13:07,912 --> 00:13:10,206
Team White Tiger's off to a good start.

224
00:13:10,999 --> 00:13:12,375
TEAM BLACK TORTOISE

225
00:13:12,458 --> 00:13:14,460
Should I try holding their hands?

226
00:13:14,961 --> 00:13:16,629
Yeah, go for it.

227
00:13:16,713 --> 00:13:18,923
Then I'll go and check their hands.

228
00:13:20,383 --> 00:13:22,343
Plum Blossom's fired up, isn't he?

229
00:13:23,803 --> 00:13:27,015
If you don't mind, may I feel your pulse?

230
00:13:28,558 --> 00:13:29,600
Excuse me.

231
00:13:30,268 --> 00:13:32,061
I checked their pulses

232
00:13:32,854 --> 00:13:34,814
because women
who've given birth many times

233
00:13:34,897 --> 00:13:36,941
have an extra pulse that signals life.

234
00:13:42,905 --> 00:13:46,159
Most importantly, I feel a jigi in my stomach.

235
00:13:46,242 --> 00:13:49,370
COUPLE 9 KIM HYEONGU,
YEO EUNGYEONG

236
00:13:49,454 --> 00:13:52,582
When I felt her pulse, I felt
a tearing sensation in my lower stomach.

237
00:13:53,082 --> 00:13:56,586
I physically felt she'd given birth.

238
00:13:56,669 --> 00:13:57,754
Thank you.

239
00:13:58,463 --> 00:13:59,547
Ouch, my back.

240
00:14:03,134 --> 00:14:05,511
- Looks like he has back pain.
- He's gripping his waist.

241
00:14:05,595 --> 00:14:07,221
He's sensing multiple pregnancies,
that's why.

242
00:14:07,305 --> 00:14:08,306
Oh! Ah!

243
00:14:08,389 --> 00:14:10,516
- Birthing pains.
- Is that it?

244
00:14:19,484 --> 00:14:21,694
- He's got his cloth out.
- Mmm.

245
00:14:22,445 --> 00:14:24,530
- He's tying it up.
- Yes.

246
00:14:25,364 --> 00:14:28,117
Last time, I prepared
a goppae

247
00:14:28,201 --> 00:14:30,578
for a deceased who died tragically.

248
00:14:30,661 --> 00:14:33,998
I used a white goppae this time.

249
00:14:35,541 --> 00:14:38,920
It's like the pure white cloth
used for baby diapers back in the day.

250
00:14:39,003 --> 00:14:42,590
We do rites with pure white cloth
for the Chilseong deity,

251
00:14:42,673 --> 00:14:45,176
who oversees babies.

252
00:14:47,637 --> 00:14:50,223
I held pure white cloth
in front of the couples

253
00:14:50,306 --> 00:14:51,557
to see if I could feel babies.

254
00:14:51,641 --> 00:14:54,268
I closed my eyes
to see if I'd get any visions.

255
00:14:58,481 --> 00:15:00,858
COUPLE 10 HAN GYEONGMIN,
PARK JIYEON

256
00:15:05,404 --> 00:15:06,447
I hear crying.

257
00:15:07,323 --> 00:15:10,076
