Seolhwa.

1025
00:54:37,983 --> 00:54:40,444
She looks like a Heavenly Fairy.

1026
00:54:41,528 --> 00:54:44,198
She's straightforward.
She says what she sees and feels.

1027
00:54:44,281 --> 00:54:46,909
She speaks freely, no filter.

1028
00:54:46,992 --> 00:54:48,327
The schizophrenia's long gone.

1029
00:54:48,410 --> 00:54:50,871
Bring her to me. She'll listen to a woman.

1030
00:54:50,954 --> 00:54:52,122
I was so impressed.

1031
00:54:52,206 --> 00:54:55,584
She's eloquent, doesn't hesitate,
and is very confident.

1032
00:54:56,168 --> 00:54:58,921
Let's win this, no matter what.

1033
00:55:00,506 --> 00:55:02,299
The second survivor.

1034
00:55:03,133 --> 00:55:04,927
A shaman with 20 years of experience

1035
00:55:05,010 --> 00:55:06,637
who consoles your hearts

1036
00:55:06,720 --> 00:55:09,139
with profound readings.

1037
00:55:09,223 --> 00:55:10,349
Lee Sobin.

1038
00:55:11,642 --> 00:55:14,353
She looks extra charismatic today.

1039
00:55:15,687 --> 00:55:19,191
She's very charismatic
when she's reading fortunes.

1040
00:55:19,274 --> 00:55:21,443
Her aura is extraordinary, for sure.

1041
00:55:22,194 --> 00:55:25,447
I've come this far,
so let me win this thing.

1042
00:55:26,365 --> 00:55:28,784
She has this fierce energy.

1043
00:55:29,493 --> 00:55:31,411
The third survivor.

1044
00:55:33,247 --> 00:55:35,457
- Ooh.
- A staff?

1045
00:55:36,291 --> 00:55:40,003
A tarot master with unparalleled charisma.

1046
00:55:40,587 --> 00:55:41,588
Monad.

1047
00:55:41,672 --> 00:55:43,090
MONAD
8-YEAR TAROT MASTER

1048
00:55:44,049 --> 00:55:46,343
Her tarot reading skill is remarkable.

1049
00:55:46,426 --> 00:55:48,303
Tarot masters are no easy mark too.

1050
00:55:48,387 --> 00:55:49,888
Homeless people have no homes.

1051
00:55:49,972 --> 00:55:53,016
For number 4,
the card suggests they're without a home.

1052
00:55:53,642 --> 00:55:55,978
I came here to win.

1053
00:55:56,562 --> 00:56:00,440
I'll show you what East Asian tarot
is capable of today.

1054
00:56:01,024 --> 00:56:02,109
The fourth survivor.

1055
00:56:05,696 --> 00:56:07,864
Pansori
singer with spiritual powers.

1056
00:56:07,948 --> 00:56:10,075
Five-year singer-shaman.

1057
00:56:11,034 --> 00:56:12,035
Yoon Daeman.

1058
00:56:12,119 --> 00:56:13,912
YOON DAEMAN
5-YEAR SHAMAN

1059
00:56:15,247 --> 00:56:18,125
His readings are quite impactful.

1060
00:56:18,208 --> 00:56:22,629
There are thieves and rats
with big eyes and big feet.

1061
00:56:22,713 --> 00:56:24,214
All sorts of thieves and rats.

1062
00:56:24,298 --> 00:56:26,675
He tells fortunes as if he's singing,

1063
00:56:26,758 --> 00:56:28,468
and that itself is very intimidating.

1064
00:56:29,052 --> 00:56:32,264
I'll show you
the skills I've honed over the years.

1065
00:56:33,473 --> 00:56:35,601
The fifth survivor.

1066
00:56:35,684 --> 00:56:40,480
A Gen Z shaman with 26 years of experience
that was born to be a shaman.

1067
00:56:41,064 --> 00:56:42,941
Manshin Kwon Sujin.

1068
00:56:44,693 --> 00:56:45,986
She's warm and gentle,

1069
00:56:46,069 --> 00:56:49,448
but she has that firmness
that comes from experience.

1070
00:56:50,032 --> 00:56:53,368
This person had to live
away from home since he was young.

1071
00:56:53,452 --> 00:56:56,038
Cash rolling around in his palms.

1072
00:56:56,121 --> 00:56:59,708
Manshins have the skills
that befit their experience.

1073
00:56:59,791 --> 00:57:02,210
I've got this far,
so I'm determined to win.

1074
00:57:03,420 --> 00:57:05,922
The sixth survivor.

1075
00:57:09,426 --> 00:57:12,971
The tarot master
who reads fates with spiritual power.

1076
00:57:13,055 --> 00:57:14,056
Choi Hannah.

1077
00:57:16,433 --> 00:57:18,727
She's a spiritual tarot card master.

1078
00:57:18,810 --> 00:57:20,103
She's basically a shaman.

1079
00:57:20,937 --> 00:57:24,399
The wife's cards show fire,
so she gets pregnant easily.

1080
00:57:24,483 --> 00:57:26,068
A one-shot, one-kill situation.

1081
00:57:26,151 --> 00:57:27,736
I'm positive.

1082
00:57:27,819 --> 00:57:30,489
I'm sure I can beat everyone and move up.

1083
00:57:30,572 --> 00:57:31,782
I'm confident.

1084
00:57:32,574 --> 00:57:35,869
Today's competition
will be a fun one to watch.

1085
00:57:38,246 --> 00:57:40,332
Battle of Fates.

1086
00:57:41,041 --> 00:57:42,793
The fourth round is…

1087
00:57:44,461 --> 00:57:47,005
…the Battle of Gods.

1088
00:57:47,881 --> 00:57:50,884
With the power of the spirits and deities,

1089
00:57:50,967 --> 00:57:53,679
we hope to look into a person's fate.

1090
00:57:55,263 --> 00:57:56,640
In the Battle of Gods,

1091
00:57:57,224 --> 00:57:59,184
2 Fate Readers

1092
00:57:59,267 --> 00:58:04,147
will go head-to-head
to read 1 person's fortune.

1093
00:58:04,231 --> 00:58:06,358
- A 1-on-1 face-off?
- Whoa…

1094
00:58:06,441 --> 00:58:07,818
This is the most fun.

1095
00:58:08,402 --> 00:58:09,736
Two people reading together?

1096
00:58:09,820 --> 00:58:13,782
Reading 1 person at the same time
felt like good fun.

1097
00:58:14,324 --> 00:58:17,411
I'm pretty confident at reading fortunes.

1098
00:58:18,036 --> 00:58:22,541
I did think I'd survive,
regardless of who I go up against.

1099
00:58:23,542 --> 00:58:26,503
Three well-known public figures

1100
00:58:26,586 --> 00:58:30,048
joined Battle of Fates

1101
00:58:30,674 --> 00:58:32,634
to seek advice

1102
00:58:33,260 --> 00:58:36,221
on tricky questions
about their personal lives.

1103
00:58:36,304 --> 00:58:37,723
BORN ON SEPTEMBER 28, 1985, MALE
BORN ON MAY 11, 1965, FEMALE

1104
00:58:37,806 --> 00:58:38,807
BORN ON JULY 3, 1983, FEMALE

1105
00:58:39,391 --> 00:58:42,894
The 3 people have selected

1106
00:58:42,978 --> 00:58:45,355
2 Fate Readers they wish to seek

1107
00:58:45,439 --> 00:58:47,941
a fate reading from.

1108
00:58:48,024 --> 00:58:50,068
Oh…

1109
00:58:54,448 --> 00:58:55,490
Born in 1985.

1110
00:58:56,283 --> 00:58:57,659
May 11, 1965.

1111
00:58:58,160 --> 00:59:00,328
July 3, 1983.

1112
00:59:01,079 --> 00:59:05,083
After the Battle of Gods…

1113
00:59:11,298 --> 00:59:14,050
…only 3 people will survive.

1114
00:59:16,052 --> 00:59:18,638
Another half goes home.

1115
00:59:19,306 --> 00:59:21,183
All I want is to win.

1116
00:59:21,767 --> 00:59:23,185
I trust my Granny spirit.

1117
00:59:23,935 --> 00:59:26,021
I must trust my deities
and charge forward.

1118
00:59:26,104 --> 00:59:28,231
Let's just do my best.

1119
00:59:28,315 --> 00:59:31,526
I'll show you
what real spiritual tarot is.

1120
00:59:32,235 --> 00:59:35,155
I'm confident I won't lose.

1121
00:59:37,449 --> 00:59:39,242
The Battle of Gods.

1122
00:59:40,035 --> 00:59:42,621
Let the match begin.

1123
00:59:44,372 --> 00:59:45,874
I'm curious.

1124
00:59:47,125 --> 00:59:49,211
This is the first person for you to read.

1125
00:59:49,795 --> 00:59:51,213
Please enter.

1126
00:59:52,798 --> 00:59:54,549
A man born in 1985.

1127
00:59:54,633 --> 00:59:56,885
- A famous person born in 1985…
- Someone famous?

1128
00:59:56,968 --> 00:59:58,762
We must all know him.

1129
00:59:58,845 --> 01:00:01,348
Someone's here? Oh, he's coming out.

1130
01:00:09,272 --> 01:00:10,732
- Whoa.
- How cool.

1131
01:00:12,025 --> 01:00:13,485
- It's so bright.
- Where is he?

1132
01:00:16,196 --> 01:00:18,031
- Gosh.
- Someone's coming.

1133
01:00:18,114 --> 01:00:19,866
- Huh? Hang on.
- Who is it?

1134
01:00:19,950 --> 01:00:21,785
What?

1135
01:00:27,707 --> 01:00:29,084
- Huh? Hang on.
- Who is it?

1136
01:00:29,167 --> 01:00:30,836
It's you, Shindong?

1137
01:00:31,586 --> 01:00:33,338
- Huh? Huh?
- What's this?

1138
01:00:33,421 --> 01:00:35,382
What are you doing down there?

1139
01:00:35,465 --> 01:00:36,716
Hello. I'm Shindong.

1140
01:00:39,261 --> 01:00:41,513
LONG-RUNNING LEGENDS OF K-POP

1141
01:00:41,596 --> 01:00:44,432
SUPER JUNIOR,
THE ROLE MODEL OF K-POP IDOLS

1142
01:00:45,016 --> 01:00:46,810
THE FIRST FATE TO READ
SHINDONG

1143
01:00:48,061 --> 01:00:49,521
- No way.
- Is this for real?

1144
01:00:50,689 --> 01:00:54,901
What… Why is he coming out of there?

1145
01:00:54,985 --> 01:00:56,778
Why is he down here?

1146
01:00:57,404 --> 01:01:00,532
- Didn't he say he had a gig?
- You said you had…

1147
01:01:00,615 --> 01:01:01,741
You had personal business.

1148
01:01:01,825 --> 01:01:03,577
-Another gig.
-He said he'd be abroad.

1149
01:01:04,536 --> 01:01:06,872
It wouldn't be fun if you knew,

1150
01:01:06,955 --> 01:01:08,832
and I thought the Fate Readers

1151
01:01:08,915 --> 01:01:11,293
should be clueless
in order to give me a reading properly.

1152
01:01:11,376 --> 01:01:13,378
I'm sorry, but I lied.

1153
01:01:15,297 --> 01:01:18,383
You all know.
Anyone up there knows the feeling.

1154
01:01:23,388 --> 01:01:24,806
You want to be down here.

1155
01:01:24,890 --> 01:01:26,975
- We said that a hundred times.
- I'd love to.

1156
01:01:27,058 --> 01:01:28,310
Yes, I'm jealous.

1157
01:01:28,393 --> 01:01:30,437
I want those 2 people to read my fortune.

1158
01:01:30,520 --> 01:01:32,814
It must be fun. I want to be down there.

1159
01:01:32,898 --> 01:01:34,316
-I'm really curious.
-Same.

1160
01:01:34,399 --> 01:01:36,651
I really want to give it a go.

1161
01:01:36,735 --> 01:01:37,986
I want to look from up close.

1162
01:01:38,069 --> 01:01:40,363
I'd try to guess
if I didn't know the answer.

1163
01:01:41,281 --> 01:01:42,699
This is insane.

1164
01:01:42,782 --> 01:01:44,951
I wanted to have my fortune read,

1165
01:01:45,035 --> 01:01:48,246
so today, I came down here myself.

1166
01:01:49,497 --> 01:01:52,375
But that's not the only reason.

1167
01:01:52,459 --> 01:01:54,586
You have an actual question, right?

1168
01:01:54,669 --> 01:01:57,839
Yes. Being a celebrity

1169
01:01:57,923 --> 01:02:00,467
means you're bound to be
anxious about the future.

1170
01:02:00,550 --> 01:02:03,511
I know what happened in my past,

1171
01:02:03,595 --> 01:02:06,514
but I really want to know
what lies ahead of me.

1172
01:02:06,598 --> 01:02:09,684
I'm getting older now too,

1173
01:02:09,768 --> 01:02:11,811
- and I'm curious about marriage.
- Oh, dear.

1174
01:02:12,312 --> 01:02:14,105
I love children,

1175
01:02:14,189 --> 01:02:16,733
so I wonder how many I'll have.

1176
01:02:17,943 --> 01:02:22,739
I believe you chose
2 Fate Readers, Shindong.

1177
01:02:22,822 --> 01:02:25,325
-Is that true?
-Yes. I've chosen 2 Fate Readers.

1178
01:02:29,329 --> 01:02:31,748
The first fate for you to read
is Shindong's fate.

1179
01:02:32,457 --> 01:02:35,293
He chose the following Fate Readers.

1180
01:02:42,592 --> 01:02:43,635
Seolhwa.

1181
01:02:43,718 --> 01:02:44,886
SEOLHWA
4-YEAR SHAMAN

1182
01:02:44,970 --> 01:02:46,096
And

1183
01:02:46,179 --> 01:02:47,722
Choi Hannah.

1184
01:02:47,806 --> 01:02:49,265
CHOI HANNAH
3-YEAR TAROT MASTER

1185
01:02:50,642 --> 01:02:51,643
Oh…

1186
01:02:52,936 --> 01:02:54,104
Why Hannah?

1187
01:02:55,105 --> 01:02:58,191
Sobin, Hannah, and I

1188
01:02:58,274 --> 01:03:00,652
had become allies before we even knew it.

1189
01:03:00,735 --> 01:03:03,863
But now we've become opponents.

1190
01:03:03,947 --> 01:03:06,366
It didn't feel nice, to be honest.

1191
01:03:06,449 --> 01:03:09,911
Ah, I found it so cruel.

1192
01:03:10,745 --> 01:03:13,164
This is fate. We're fated.

1193
01:03:13,748 --> 01:03:17,961
We helped and rooted for
each other during the third round,

1194
01:03:18,044 --> 01:03:20,380
and now we must go head-to-head.

1195
01:03:20,463 --> 01:03:23,466
Ah, what twist of fate is this?

1196
01:03:24,968 --> 01:03:28,221
- Yesterday's comrades…
- Yes. It can't be helped.

1197
01:03:28,304 --> 01:03:29,806
We can have only 1 winner.

1198
01:03:33,351 --> 01:03:37,022
Seolhwa will give a reading first.

1199
01:03:37,105 --> 01:03:38,565
Seolhwa first.

1200
01:03:38,648 --> 01:03:41,901
To avoid being influenced
by Seolhwa's reading,

1201
01:03:41,985 --> 01:03:45,947
Hannah, please put on the headset.

1202
01:03:47,073 --> 01:03:49,492
They're making sure she doesn't hear
Seolhwa's reading.

1203
01:03:49,576 --> 01:03:51,870
Ah, so she can't hear the other reading.

1204
01:03:53,038 --> 01:03:54,706
THE FATE READER ON STANDBY

1205
01:03:54,789 --> 01:03:57,000
WEARS A HEADSET TO AVOID LISTENING IN

1206
01:03:57,083 --> 01:03:58,877
How interesting.

1207
01:04:00,879 --> 01:04:04,466
The final round is coming up.
I should win no matter what.

1208
01:04:04,549 --> 01:04:06,051
Let's not feel intimidated.

1209
01:04:06,760 --> 01:04:10,180
Seolhwa, please begin your reading.

1210
01:04:11,056 --> 01:04:12,348
Your real name, please.

1211
01:04:12,849 --> 01:04:15,810
My real name is Shin Donghee.

1212
01:04:16,352 --> 01:04:17,687
I feel nervous now.

1213
01:04:21,274 --> 01:04:24,652
Granny, Grandpa, this is Shindong.

1214
01:04:24,736 --> 01:04:26,738
His real name is Shin Donghee.

1215
01:04:26,821 --> 01:04:30,075
He was born in 1985, the Year of the Ox.

1216
01:04:30,158 --> 01:04:34,621
Help me relay the right message
without my human thoughts.

1217
01:04:35,121 --> 01:04:37,582
From 1 to 2, from 2 to 3.

1218
01:04:42,253 --> 01:04:44,798
You say you want to marry

1219
01:04:44,881 --> 01:04:46,633
and want to meet women,

1220
01:04:46,716 --> 01:04:48,426
but no one's up to your standards.

1221
01:04:48,510 --> 01:04:50,512
Hmm…

1222
01:04:55,016 --> 01:04:57,811
I think you're only saying
that you want to date and marry.

1223
01:04:57,894 --> 01:05:00,522
You don't trust women.

1224
01:05:00,605 --> 01:05:04,192
You need a younger woman who's mature.

1225
01:05:04,275 --> 01:05:06,194
Even a 12-year age gap is fine.

1226
01:05:07,278 --> 01:05:08,530
- Is that okay?
- Yes.

1227
01:05:08,613 --> 01:05:10,657
He said, "Is that okay?"

1228
01:05:10,740 --> 01:05:12,450
- He can't hide his joy.
- He seems so happy.

1229
01:05:12,534 --> 01:05:14,828
- He seems over the moon.
- So happy.

1230
01:05:15,578 --> 01:05:18,957
An age gap of 12 to 15 years is fine.

1231
01:05:19,040 --> 01:05:20,291
- Oh.
- But…

1232
01:05:20,375 --> 01:05:24,170
But you can't stand
younger girls that act like a baby.

1233
01:05:24,254 --> 01:05:26,589
And you can't stand a housewife
who doesn't work.

1234
01:05:26,673 --> 01:05:30,009
You're better off with someone active
that manages and maintains her own life

1235
01:05:30,093 --> 01:05:32,428
and brings in an income together.

1236
01:05:32,512 --> 01:05:34,597
I'm so surprised right now.

1237
01:05:34,681 --> 01:05:37,934
I thought she was talking about my ex.

1238
01:05:38,017 --> 01:05:39,394
She hit the nail on the head.

1239
01:05:40,520 --> 01:05:43,273
She got everything right,
from the age. Everything.

1240
01:05:43,356 --> 01:05:45,733
I don't know who your ex is,

1241
01:05:45,817 --> 01:05:47,569
but you almost married her, right?

1242
01:05:49,237 --> 01:05:51,865
You almost got married,

1243
01:05:52,365 --> 01:05:54,200
but it looks like the timing was off.

1244
01:05:54,284 --> 01:05:55,535
- She's right.
- Yes.

1245
01:05:55,618 --> 01:05:57,745
- That's true.
- She's right. For real.

1246
01:05:57,829 --> 01:05:58,997
You guys know about it.

1247
01:05:59,706 --> 01:06:00,707
You know.

1248
01:06:00,790 --> 01:06:03,042
-I know.
-I know too.

1249
01:06:03,126 --> 01:06:04,127
Oh…

1250
01:06:04,210 --> 01:06:06,588
You almost married her.
Your ancestors were in agreement.

1251
01:06:06,671 --> 01:06:08,256
- Yes.
- You could've had a baby too,

1252
01:06:08,339 --> 01:06:10,383
but you broke up
because something didn't go right.

1253
01:06:18,141 --> 01:06:19,434
You said your grandmother is a shaman.

1254
01:06:19,517 --> 01:06:22,437
-Which side of the family?
-My paternal grandmother.

1255
01:06:22,520 --> 01:06:25,940
When she passes away…

1256
01:06:26,024 --> 01:06:28,026
When she passes away…

1257
01:06:29,277 --> 01:06:31,654
It might be dangerous for you.

1258
01:06:31,738 --> 01:06:32,947
What does that mean?

1259
01:06:33,031 --> 01:06:35,909
Someone's trying to make you hold bells.

1260
01:06:35,992 --> 01:06:37,118
Bells?

1261
01:06:37,202 --> 01:06:39,704
Someone wants you to become a shaman.

1262
01:06:39,787 --> 01:06:41,372
- Oh, no.
- Gosh.

1263
01:06:42,665 --> 01:06:44,834
- To become a shaman?
- He'll get the calling.

1264
01:06:44,918 --> 01:06:47,545
- I got goosebumps.
- Oh, dear…

1265
01:06:49,672 --> 01:06:52,884
You must be careful.
I'm not saying you'll become a shaman,

1266
01:06:52,967 --> 01:06:54,969
but it runs in your family.

1267
01:06:55,053 --> 01:06:57,096
You're bound to feel the pain.

1268
01:06:57,180 --> 01:07:00,725
You have powerful ancestors,
and there's a shaman in the family,

1269
01:07:00,808 --> 01:07:02,477
and you have shaman ancestors too.

1270
01:07:02,560 --> 01:07:05,480
And 1 of the shaman ancestors
will touch you.

1271
01:07:08,024 --> 01:07:10,568
He definitely has that shamanic gift.

1272
01:07:10,652 --> 01:07:11,736
I can't say who,

1273
01:07:11,819 --> 01:07:15,698
but he told a girl group member
to be careful as he felt something,

1274
01:07:15,782 --> 01:07:17,200
- and a scandal broke out.
- Yes.

1275
01:07:17,283 --> 01:07:18,826
He does have that spiritual power.

1276
01:07:19,786 --> 01:07:22,080
Because you have
the tendencies of a shaman,

1277
01:07:22,163 --> 01:07:25,917
you sing and dance in public
to stave some of it off

1278
01:07:26,000 --> 01:07:28,920
and it's true that it's helping somewhat.

1279
01:07:29,003 --> 01:07:30,004
But…

1280
01:07:31,172 --> 01:07:32,173
But…

1281
01:07:33,466 --> 01:07:36,427
The way I see it,
it's nowhere near enough.

1282
01:07:36,511 --> 01:07:38,596
Your luck in business opens up this year.

1283
01:07:38,680 --> 01:07:40,598
Your luck in business opens up this year.

1284
01:07:42,267 --> 01:07:43,935
2025, AGED 40, GOT AN OFFER
TO START A BUSINESS

1285
01:07:44,018 --> 01:07:45,895
Oh…

1286
01:07:45,979 --> 01:07:46,980
My gosh.

1287
01:07:47,897 --> 01:07:51,192
